org.mobicents.slee.container.transaction
Interface SleeTransactionManager

All Superinterfaces:
SleeContainerModule, javax.slee.transaction.SleeTransactionManager, javax.transaction.TransactionManager
public interface SleeTransactionManager
extends SleeContainerModule, javax.slee.transaction.SleeTransactionManager

Transaction manager contract within SLEE. Provides convenience methods for tx and its context handling.

Author:
M. Ranganathan, Ivelin Ivanov, martins

requireTransactionEnd

void requireTransactionEnd(boolean terminateTx,
                           boolean doRollback)
                           throws java.lang.IllegalStateException,
                                  java.lang.SecurityException,
                                  javax.transaction.SystemException,
                                  javax.transaction.RollbackException,
                                  javax.transaction.HeuristicMixedException,
                                  javax.transaction.HeuristicRollbackException
Executes logic to complete the handling of a slee transaction by a method that requires a tx context. to be used as a complement of requireTransaction()

Parameters:
terminateTx - indicates if the logic should terminate the tx or not
doRollback - if true indicates a rollback should be done, either by terminating the tx with rollback() or by just setting the rollback only flag
txManager - the tx manager to use
Throws:
javax.slee.SLEEException - if the transaction can't be finalized
